				<div class="title-block">
					
						<h3 class="title" id="posttitle_37117248"><a href="http://iunknown.com/2008/05/ironruby-and-rails.html">IronRuby and Rails</a></h3>
					
					
						<ul class="meta">
							<li class="date">30 May 2008</li>
